    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-details">
        <summary>What are signs my AC needs repair?</summary>
        <div class="faq-details-body">
          <p>Common signs include: weak airflow, warm air blowing, strange noises (grinding, squealing, rattling), unusual odors, water leaks, frequent cycling on/off, or rising energy bills. If you notice any of these, call (808) 664-5751 for fast diagnosis and repair.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-details">
        <summary>Do you offer same-day AC repair?</summary>
        <div class="faq-details-body">
          <p>Yes! We understand Hawaii's heat is unbearable without AC. We offer same-day service for emergency repairs whenever possible. Call (808) 664-5751 and we'll do our best to get you cool again today.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-details">
        <summary>How often should I service my AC in Hawaii?</summary>
        <div class="faq-details-body">
          <p>We recommend annual maintenance, ideally before the hot season. Hawaii's humid climate and salt air are tough on AC equipment. Regular maintenance prevents breakdowns, improves efficiency, and extends system life.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-details">
        <summary>How much does AC repair cost?</summary>
        <div class="faq-details-body">
          <p>Repair costs vary depending on the problem. Simple fixes like thermostat issues or filter changes are inexpensive. Major repairs like compressor replacement cost more. We provide upfront quotes before starting any work so you know exactly what to expect.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-details">
        <summary>Can I do AC maintenance myself?</summary>
        <div class="faq-details-body">
          <p>You can handle basic tasks like changing filters and keeping outdoor units clear of debris. However, professional maintenance includes refrigerant checks, electrical testing, and coil cleaning that require specialized tools and licensing. Annual professional service is worth the investment.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-details">
        <summary>Do you work on all AC brands?</summary>
        <div class="faq-details-body">
          <p>Yes! We service and repair all major brands including Daikin, Mitsubishi, Carrier, Trane, Lennox, Fujitsu, LG, and more. We work on mini-splits, central air, heat pumps, and all system types.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

